official-title.#text: To redesignate Rock Creek Park in the District of Columbia as Rock Creek National Park in the District of Columbia.

header.#text: Redesignation of Rock Creek Park As Rock Creek National Park in the District of Columbia

text.#text: In recognition of its nationally significant natural, cultural, and historical resources, and important recreational opportunities, Rock Creek Park in the District of Columbia, established by the

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#tail: , is redesignated as Rock Creek National Park in the District of Columbia.
